> 
> Anyway, I have patched the 2.6.20 kernel and have a partition formatted
> with Reiser4.
> 
> However, I am having trouble getting LILO or GRUB working (with
> Reiser4).
> 
> Could you guys who know all about this, help me, or point me to some
